  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Roflumilast in Japanese Patients With Bronchial Asthma (20 to 70 y) (APTA-2217-05)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Confirmatory Study of APTA-2217 in Adult Patients With Bronchial Asthma (A Placebo-controlled Double-blind Comparative Study)</official_title>
